ZH: 我会把这个石头看成是一片珊瑚。
EN: I will see this rock as a piece of coral.

ZH: 我总是把她的微笑看成是对我最好的礼物。
EN: I always see her smile as the best gift to me.

ZH: 他把每个问题都看成是一个机会。
EN: He sees every problem as an opportunity.

ZH: 她总是把伤心的事看成一种成长的机会。
EN: She always sees sad events as opportunities for growth.

ZH: 他把所有人的言论都看成了一个笑话。
EN: He sees everyone's remarks as a joke.

ZH: 你不能把本书看成一本小说。
EN: You can't see this book as a novel.

